00:26:40.932 --> 00:26:42.683
Kako, za vraga, bodo izpluli?

00:26:42.852 --> 00:26:45.729
Zato mislim, da moramo
splaviti rešilne čolne.

00:26:45.855 --> 00:26:47.521
Zmanjkuje nam sreče.

00:26:47.606 --> 00:26:49.040
Ne verjamem v srečo, Brown.

00:26:49.107 --> 00:26:51.526
